{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-06",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_06_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 6 - The Undersized Shadow",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 4,
  "page_total": 5,
  "page_start_sec": 737.38,
  "page_end_sec": 981.22,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.735,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 737.38,
      "end": 739.4,
      "text": "Their faces were a few inches apart.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 740.2,
      "end": 742.46,
      "text": "Spade took her face between his hands and he",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 742.46,
      "end": 744.42,
      "text": "kissed her mouth roughly and contemptuously."
    },
    {
      "start": 745.64,
      "end": 746.88,
      "text": "Then he sat back and said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 747.872,
      "end": 748.74,
      "text": "\"'I'll think it over.'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 749.38,
      "end": 751.3,
      "text": "His face was hard and furious."
    },
    {
      "start": 752.74,
      "end": 753.5,
      "text": "She sat still,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 753.7,
      "end": 756.28,
      "text": "holding her numb face where his hands had left it."
    },
    {
      "start": 757.0,
      "end": 758.36,
      "text": "He stood up and said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 759.44,
      "end": 760.96,
      "text": "There's no sense to this.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 762.02,
      "end": 764.16,
      "text": "He took two steps toward the fireplace and stopped,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 764.52,
      "end": 765.92,
      "text": "glowering at the burning logs,"
    },
    {
      "start": 766.12,
      "end": 767.3,
      "text": "grinding his teeth together."
    },
    {
      "start": 768.4,
      "end": 769.3,
      "text": "She did not move.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 770.42,
      "end": 771.44,
      "text": "He turned to face her.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 772.14,
      "end": 773.88,
      "text": "The two vertical lines over her nose"
    },
    {
      "start": 773.88,
      "end": 775.84,
      "text": "were deep clefts between red welts."
    },
    {
      "start": 777.03,
      "end": 780.58,
      "text": "\"'I don't give a damn about your honesty,' he told her,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 780.6,
      "end": 782.26,
      "text": "trying to make himself speak calmly."
    },
    {
      "start": 782.94,
      "end": 784.66,
      "text": "\"'I don't care what kind of tricks"
    },
    {
      "start": 784.66,
      "end": 786.68,
      "text": "you're up to or what your secrets are."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.52,
      "end": 788.34,
      "text": "But I've got to have",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 788.46,
      "end": 790.74,
      "text": "something to show that you know what you're doing.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 791.62,
      "end": 792.2,
      "text": "\"'I do know.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 792.38,
      "end": 794.06,
      "text": "Please believe that I do,"
    },
    {
      "start": 794.22,
      "end": 795.92,
      "text": "and that it's all for the best."
    },
    {
      "start": 796.15,
      "end": 798.34,
      "text": "And—' \"'Show me,' he ordered."
    },
    {
      "start": 799.2,
      "end": 800.08,
      "text": "\"'I'm willing to help you.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 800.704,
      "end": 802.14,
      "text": "I've done what I could so far."
    },
    {
      "start": 802.48,
      "end": 803.5,
      "text": "If necessary,"
    },
    {
      "start": 803.84,
      "end": 805.04,
      "text": "I'll go ahead blindfolded,"
    },
    {
      "start": 805.44,
      "end": 807.94,
      "text": "but I can't do it without confidence in you."
    },
    {
      "start": 809.152,
      "end": 811.16,
      "text": "You've got to convince me that you know what",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 811.16,
      "end": 811.78,
      "text": "it's all about,"
    },
    {
      "start": 811.98,
      "end": 813.86,
      "text": "that you're not simply fiddling around"
    },
    {
      "start": 813.86,
      "end": 816.88,
      "text": "by guess and by God hoping it'll come out"
    },
    {
      "start": 816.88,
      "end": 818.32,
      "text": "all right somehow in the end."
    },
    {
      "start": 819.936,
      "end": 821.58,
      "text": "Can't you trust me just a little longer?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 823.18,
      "end": 824.14,
      "text": "How much is a little?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 824.86,
      "end": 826.0,
      "text": "And what are you waiting for?"
    },
    {
      "start": 827.32,
      "end": 828.68,
      "text": "She bit her lip and looked down.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 829.35,
      "end": 832.06,
      "text": "I must talk to Joel Cairo,\""
    },
    {
      "start": 832.64,
      "end": 834.04,
      "text": "she said almost inaudibly."
    },
    {
      "start": 835.18,
      "end": 837.18,
      "text": "You can see him to-night,\" Spade said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 837.3,
      "end": 838.14,
      "text": "looking at his watch."
    },
    {
      "start": 839.12,
      "end": 840.74,
      "text": "His show will be out in a little while.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 841.44,
      "end": 843.08,
      "text": "We can get him on the phone at his hotel."
    },
    {
      "start": 844.58,
      "end": 845.52,
      "text": "She raised her eyes,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 845.56,
      "end": 846.02,
      "text": "alarmed."
    },
    {
      "start": 846.784,
      "end": 848.1,
      "text": "But he can't come here.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 848.78,
      "end": 850.32,
      "text": "I can't let him know where I am."
    },
    {
      "start": 850.42,
      "end": 851.4,
      "text": "I'm afraid."
    },
    {
      "start": 852.64,
      "end": 854.44,
      "text": "My place,\" Spade suggested.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 855.66,
      "end": 856.46,
      "text": "She hesitated,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 856.58,
      "end": 857.6,
      "text": "working her lips together,"
    },
    {
      "start": 857.84,
      "end": 858.52,
      "text": "then asked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 858.72,
      "end": 860.896,
      "text": "Do you think he'd come there?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 861.664,
      "end": 862.32,
      "text": "Spade nodded.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 863.32,
      "end": 863.6,
      "text": "All right,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 863.76,
      "end": 864.9,
      "text": "she exclaimed,"
    },
    {
      "start": 864.9,
      "end": 865.56,
      "text": "jumping up,"
    },
    {
      "start": 865.64,
      "end": 867.22,
      "text": "her eyes large and bright."
    },
    {
      "start": 868.18,
      "end": 868.88,
      "text": "Shall we go now?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 870.26,
      "end": 871.58,
      "text": "She went into the next room.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 872.384,
      "end": 874.02,
      "text": "Spade went to the table in the corner",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 874.02,
      "end": 875.94,
      "text": "and silently pulled the drawer out."
    },
    {
      "start": 876.8,
      "end": 878.78,
      "text": "The drawer held two packs of playing cards,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 879.26,
      "end": 880.43,
      "text": "a pad of bridge scorecards,"
    },
    {
      "start": 881.02,
      "end": 881.86,
      "text": "a brass screw,"
    },
    {
      "start": 882.14,
      "end": 883.36,
      "text": "a piece of red string,"
    },
    {
      "start": 883.52,
      "end": 884.34,
      "text": "and a gold pencil."
    },
    {
      "start": 885.09,
      "end": 887.78,
      "text": "He had closed the drawer and was lighting a cigarette,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 888.26,
      "end": 889.64,
      "text": "when she returned wearing a small"
    },
    {
      "start": 889.7,
      "end": 891.64,
      "text": "dark hat and gray kid-skin coat,"
    },
    {
      "start": 891.86,
      "end": 893.46,
      "text": "carrying his hat and coat."
    },
    {
      "start": 894.86,
      "end": 896.84,
      "text": "Their taxicab drew up behind a dark sedan",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 896.84,
      "end": 899.08,
      "text": "that stood directly in front of Spade's street"
    },
    {
      "start": 899.2,
      "end": 899.32,
      "text": "door."
    },
    {
      "start": 900.544,
      "end": 902.16,
      "text": "Iva Archer was alone in the sedan,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 902.48,
      "end": 903.52,
      "text": "sitting at the wheel."
    },
    {
      "start": 904.448,
      "end": 906.3,
      "text": "Spade lifted his hat to her and went",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 906.3,
      "end": 907.92,
      "text": "indoors with Bridget O'Shaughnessy."
    },
    {
      "start": 909.0,
      "end": 909.5,
      "text": "In the lobby,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 909.66,
      "end": 911.94,
      "text": "he halted beside one of the benches and asked,"
    },
    {
      "start": 912.26,
      "end": 913.86,
      "text": "Do you mind waiting here a moment?"
    },
    {
      "start": 914.02,
      "end": 915.328,
      "text": "I won't be long.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 916.256,
      "end": 918.94,
      "text": "That's perfectly all right,\" Bridget O'Shaughnessy said,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 919.08,
      "end": 919.72,
      "text": "sitting down."
    },
    {
      "start": 920.46,
      "end": 921.44,
      "text": "You needn't hurry.\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 922.464,
      "end": 923.58,
      "text": "Spade went out to the sedan.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 924.82,
      "end": 926.16,
      "text": "When he had opened the sedan door,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 926.36,
      "end": 927.53,
      "text": "Iva spoke rapidly."
    },
    {
      "start": 928.58,
      "end": 929.4,
      "text": "I've got to talk to you,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 929.44,
      "end": 929.6,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 929.8,
      "end": 931.04,
      "text": "Can I come in?\""
    },
    {
      "start": 931.32,
      "end": 933.32,
      "text": "Her face was pale and nervous."
    },
    {
      "start": 934.26,
      "end": 934.66,
      "text": "Not now.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 935.872,
      "end": 937.98,
      "text": "Iva clicked her teeth together and asked sharply,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 938.72,
      "end": 939.26,
      "text": "Who is she?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 940.68,
      "end": 941.54,
      "text": "I have only a minute,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 941.64,
      "end": 941.84,
      "text": "Iva."
    },
    {
      "start": 942.06,
      "end": 943.46,
      "text": "\"'Spade said patiently,"
    },
    {
      "start": 944.32,
      "end": 944.88,
      "text": "\"'What is it?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 945.888,
      "end": 946.65,
      "text": "\"'Who is she?'",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 947.18,
      "end": 947.68,
      "text": "she repeated,"
    },
    {
      "start": 948.16,
      "end": 949.7,
      "text": "\"'nodding at the apartment building door."
    },
    {
      "start": 950.19,
      "end": 952.5,
      "text": "\"'He looked away from her down the street."
    },
    {
      "start": 953.46,
      "end": 955.18,
      "text": "\"'In front of a garage on the next corner,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 955.7,
      "end": 957.96,
      "text": "\"'an undersized youth of twenty or twenty-one,"
    },
    {
      "start": 958.14,
      "end": 959.62,
      "text": "\"'in neat gray cap and overcoat,"
    },
    {
      "start": 959.98,
      "end": 961.78,
      "text": "\"'loafed with his back against a wall."
    },
    {
      "start": 962.72,
      "end": 965.94,
      "text": "\"'Spade frowned and returned his gaze to Iva's insistent face.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 967.6,
      "end": 968.94,
      "text": "\"'What is the matter?' he asked.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 969.44,
      "end": 970.18,
      "text": "\"'Has anything happened?"
    },
    {
      "start": 970.57,
      "end": 972.72,
      "text": "You oughtn't be here at this time of night."
    },
    {
      "start": 974.08,
      "end": 975.24,
      "text": "I'm beginning to believe that,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 975.44,
      "end": 976.38,
      "text": "she complained."
    },
    {
      "start": 977.12,
      "end": 979.3,
      "text": "You told me I oughtn't to come to the office,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 979.48,
      "end": 981.22,
      "text": "and now I oughtn't come here."
    }
  ]
}